o.php%3FSerialNo%3D72765&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL%2F7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=7e1f33f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=72765</a><br />\n<br />\n讚揚港警「很克制」 韓國瑜國政顧問：若在美國早就血流遍地<br />\n上報快訊／李紹瑜 2019年10月05日 21:00:00<br />\n<br />\n馬英九基金會5日舉行「哪來的芒果乾?」國安問題研討會，<strong>韓國瑜國政顧問團外交組成員、政治大學東亞研究所名譽教授邱坤玄，抨擊支持香港反送中示威活動的蔡英文政府，只提港府鎮壓群眾，卻完全不看暴民的暴行活動，他認為，「香港警察的克制行動，其實是可以被讚揚的。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n呼應韓國瑜3日「選前100天記者會」，「哪來的芒果乾？」國安問題研討會邀集韓國瑜國政顧問團隊陸委會前主委蘇起、前行政院長張善政等人與會。針對香港抗爭，顧問團外交組成員邱坤玄表示，引述前美國在台協會理事主席卜睿哲的說法，香港示威者應適可而止，反送中運動至今持續4個多月時間，直到最近才發生香港警察用槍射傷群眾事件，這種事情如果是發生在美國，早就血流遍地。<br />\n<br />\n「香港警察的克制行動，其實是可以被讚揚的。」邱坤玄表示，蔡政府以為撿到「槍」，到最後卻可能變成「未爆彈」，因為如果香港暴民活動持續下去，根據一些影片可以發現，其中很多示威群眾真的是暴民，而且是有組織的，頭戴防毒面具，手持鋁棍。<br />\n<br />\n邱坤玄還說，蔡政府用所謂的「今日香港、明日台灣」，當成選舉的利器，到頭來的後果會是什麼，非常值得懷疑；邱坤玄認為，蔡英文總統3年多來的執政可以用一個字「偏」來概括，在外交上向美國一邊倒，蔡政府從來不提中國是台灣的機遇，讓台灣喪失在地緣上的關鍵位置並且被邊緣化。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:13:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警嫂，藍絲齊出賣入醫院治療示威人士，FC<br />\n<br />\n</span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LMa80dy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLMa80dy.jpg&h=3f6e71c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63fed26962a4ed4c1014e13f726bfc879a8a4982","tid":1631163,"uid":283668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:13:50.000Z","msg":"賣台賊"},{"pid":"66da738db4739668ec709181e286af542d98073d","tid":1631163,"uid":402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4106875463f0166b7e69d691affea68991af1d8b","tid":1631163,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb1ab1df3e5a4dfc5254767e7a97301e54630232","tid":1631163,"uid":52006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:01:44.000Z","msg":"比佢選到呢幾個月香港既野就會o係台灣發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:08:10.000Z","msg":"佢而家攪高雄已經攪撚到香港咁<br />\n連大港開唱都無埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:15:37.000Z","msg":"條仆街自己搞助勢講晒粗口又教d韓粉周圍屌人<br />\n之後話大港開唱低俗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c3e0487fb7e42eb317fa26311cb6179d2a9a93","tid":1631163,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6badd56b31e51445db3b72d7de4952a47dac7736","tid":1631163,"uid":262674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:16:56.000Z","msg":"佢一定好撚憎光頭佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dff40304735139e7aa4548d2eea47c789450140","tid":1631163,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:19:02.000Z","msg":"笑死"},{"pid":"b5cf58149e5bdc09615534cfc972a16df3c5224d","tid":1631163,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PMg0Rj2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPMg0Rj2.jpg&h=4ff04944&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0adfc00a6f94958d54ee2954140c417f1f95a68","tid":1631163,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ae47126551b3be53bc91faba65d782ae91d4a6","tid":1631163,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:38.000Z","msg":"(公投)你覺得勇武手足以武制暴(獅鳥)程度夠唔夠阻嚇力同狠<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631155</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0fa7739e2ee29ff00ab6465e076ceb54675821cd","tid":1631163,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"强國魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ea3f617f97ee3ec708fe48beb122629ac0dd62","tid":1631163,"uid":76133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"幫小英助攻"},{"pid":"91ffab92fc3c8955b104842d3810b8bfdbb77331","tid":1631163,"uid":8941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94226e4e498b0f2cfdee174b209c963856642ce3","tid":1631163,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"你老細阿韓總機都自身難保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n顧掂自己先啦 賣台賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47bdd41ae7584da547777702cf0f1a05c410831f","tid":1631163,"uid":175668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:26:48.000Z","msg":"美國有民主喎"},{"pid":"85e080bcfd009492c4e308c6c18c51e822ede16a","tid":1631163,"uid":52658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a34ef7c14248ef3176b62c4984eff4957cd607e7","tid":1631163,"uid":250586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"有無台灣巴絲打可以賜教一下台灣總統大選形勢如何？呢段說話我實在無法理解"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:26:51.000Z","msg":"除非而家有新聞爆出黎話蔡英文係變性人<br />\n或者佢係共諜 殺左人潛逃去台灣<br />\n如果唔係佢都贏鳩硬咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ebd6e9709cbff65c631f1cc207a47c1abd8eb1","tid":1631163,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649bf60f63bcf07e546b644f2480d4f826a33d09","tid":1631163,"uid":12989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:06.000Z","msg":"麻煩善用不推文回覆"},{"pid":"57c870765f70a910403dd4081d837e72152473d2","tid":1631163,"uid":322955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a34ef7c14248ef3176b62c4984eff4957cd607e7","tid":1631163,"uid":250586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"有無台灣巴絲打可以賜教一下台灣總統大選形勢如何？呢段說話我實在無法理解"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:32.000Z","msg":"不用理這智障了<br />\n他現在民調只有三成多<br />\n<br />\n照比例換算他可能會拿不到三百萬票<br />\n他的發言基本方向跟國台辦很接近<br />\n<br />\n偶爾裝一下才出來喊要香港兩邊冷靜對話的幹話<br />\n(林鄭對話時大家講別立蒙面法，<br />\n對話完就立了對話有屁用)<br />\n<br />\n現在在拼立委席次了<br />\n總統現在只有選輸，跟選輸很多兩個選項<br />\n<br />\n然後韓柯陣營拼命買公關公司跟鐵粉護航<br />\n搭配在台陸生鼓吹風向<br />\n<br />\n韓陣營最會講：菸粉快點推完文叫小英宣戰<br />\n                           )$&amp;@:?-'-);&quot;(  不好意思他們智商太低我翻不出來在講啥<br />\n柯陣營最會講：菸粉快點買下一班飛機去香港衝第一線<br />\n                           香港是外國事務，小波浪不用關心<br />\n                           柯P幫香港講很多話了(擦槍走火&hellip;)菸粉為什麼一直來黑<br />\n<br />\n然後講不出什麼有建設性的話<br />\n兩個人都在講幹話<br />\n<br />\n民主政治最悲慘的地方在<br />\n國民黨還是有機會不分區拿下12-15席<br />\n(韓國瑜估的，但是現況韓系人馬只要排前7就很難說了)<br />\n原住民應該六席，離島兩席<br />\n苗栗一席<br />\n台北市至少三席<br />\n新北也至少三席<br />\n關鍵在桃園跟台中能攻下多少新的席次<br />\n以上估值是低標喔&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n柯P我估可能3-5席加PFP 2席組黨團<br />\n<br />\n時力不一定，大約落在4-5席<br />\n不過他們去挖深綠牆角可能會被棄保<br />\n基進有可能區域1席不分區如果6%就有兩席<br />\n(5%才能進二輪分席次)<br />\n<br />\n民進黨要再拿69席有難度<br />\n更不用說修憲門檻85席<br />\n<br />\n如果不過半很多法案包括香港相關法案<br />\n要推國民黨都會起來搗蛋這是肯定的<br />\n然後台民黨應該會左膠跟國民黨合唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時力不當小綠的情況下也很難講下一屆立法院生態<br />\n大概是這樣"},{"pid":"9f09732d2f1f253e016e39ce41759c2bf346b4cf","tid":1631163,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57c870765f70a910403dd4081d837e72152473d2","tid":1631163,"uid":322955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a34ef7c14248ef3176b62c4984eff4957cd607e7","tid":1631163,"uid":250586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTi